g.title: j2921028588
g.text: Yeah, well. You're not exactly making me want to stick around.

g.title: j2878324086
g.text: For saying you will leave us here

g.title: j156338324
g.text: Even if it's true... Even if you do leave us someday and don't come back
I know it would be for the right reasons
I attacked you and it was wrong

g.title: j1435094556
g.text: You need to learn to stop taking your shit out on other people.

g.title: j2623219051
g.text: I... lash out when I get afraid, babas, and that is not your fault

g.title: j4216842058
g.text: I... lash out when I get afraid, babas, and that is not your fault

g.title: j1283935518
g.text: *You're* afraid of something? Holy shit, get Eleanor, we have a newspaper article to write.

g.title: j1746492160
g.text: Of no change, of no death

g.title: j2234795323
g.text: So the fact that you can just LEAVE

g.title: j3416376388
g.text: I would run as far and fast as I could from here

g.title: j2975791515
g.text: I guess because I've lived through a loop before, I'm not so scared of it.

g.title: j11238784
g.text: Yeah, but... I have something valuable keeping me here.

g.title: j447336445
g.text: But you'll get bored in time
Like Amir with his little games

g.title: j2770570721
g.text: El chamaco is surrounded by those cassettes and keeps saying he has nothing to play

g.title: j1222049259
g.text: You'll do the same to us
Toss us aside like a game you're tired of

g.title: j275449237
g.text: Because we are so special to you

g.title: j3081904445
g.text: You can choose to believe me or not.

g.title: j2082588428
g.text: I can't make promises about the future, Lettie. It hasn't been written yet.

g.title: j596755280
g.text: I'm sure you and I could find ways of keeping things interesting... ;)

g.title: j3682760104
g.text: Back to it for both of us

g.title: j174512571
g.text: I just came to say I am sorry and explain why, that is all

g.title: j4246370287
g.text: Oh, the games we could play
